OL,3,C'Losing my sight is the reason i'm
OL,4,Cclean and sober'
OL,6,FA man says he is celebrating four
OL,7,Fyears of sobriety a journey because of
OL,8,Fhis sight loss.
OL,10,FAfter battling addiction for over
OL,11,Fthree decades, Ray Clements from
OL,12,FLiverpool reached a critical moment
OL,13,Fwhen he woke up beside a vodka bottle
OL,14,Fthe morning after the diagnosis of his
OL,15,Frare genetic condition.
OL,17,F"I think I had always been an
OL,18,Falcoholic to be honest. I could drink
OL,19,F2 to 4 litres of vodka a day," Ray
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
