OL,3,C'Losing my sight is the reason i'm
OL,4,Cclean and sober'
OL,6,FToday, he dedicates his life to
OL,7,Fhelping others in the community and
OL,8,Fhas even played blind baseball for
OL,9,FGreat Britain.
OL,11,FHis guide dog Garson has also been
OL,12,Fpivotal in his new chapter, teaching
OL,13,Fhim courage and freedom.
OL,15,FRay said: "He has taught me so much".
OL,17,FRay says his sight loss is the
OL,18,Fgreatest gift of his life, pushing him
OL,19,Fto truly live and he hopes his message
OL,20,Fsparks hope in others facing their own
OL,21,Fbattles.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
