OL,3,C'Losing my sight is the reason i'm
OL,4,Cclean and sober'
OL,6,F"Losing my sight is the reason that I
OL,7,Fam clean and sober. That's the truth.
OL,8,FI was full of fear."
OL,10,FHe added: "Finding out about my mental
OL,11,Fhealth is because of my sight, playing
OL,12,Fsport is because of my sight.
OL,14,F"Sight loss is the best thing that's
OL,15,Fhappened to me. It doesn't make it
OL,16,Feasy, but it's the best thing that's
OL,17,Fhappened to me in my life. Because I'm
OL,18,Fnot existing anymore. I'm living.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
